Package: netbeans-platform
Architecture: all
Section: libs
Depends: sun-java5-bin
Description: Platform for building rich desktop applications in Java
 NetBeans Platform is the framework for building rich desktop applications
 in Java.  It is the core of the NetBeans IDE.
 .
 For more information see the project website: http://www.netbeans.org/.

Package: netbeans
Architecture: all
Depends: sun-java5-bin, netbeans-platform (=5.5), ant (>=1.6.5), tomcat5.5
Recommends:  ant-optional, ant-doc
Suggests: ant-optional, ant-doc
Description: IDE to support development of applications in Java
 NetBeans is a modern IDE which supports development of applications in the
 Java programming language.  The distinctive feature of this IDE is it tries
 hard to suppport the whole Java platform stack, out of the box.  All important
 Java standard APIs are supported out of the box.  Recently NetBeans started to
 expand its reach beyond Java to C/C++ and other programming languages as well.
 .
 For more information see the project website: http://www.netbeans.org/.
